==================================
===      INSTALLATION         ====
==================================

0) Download and install blender 2.55

1) Create a folder named "curve_to_even_mesh" under the "2.55/scripts/addons" folder in your blender data folder.

2) Copy all three files into the newly created directory

3) Enable the addon "Curve to even mesh" under the user preferences

4) Select a curve, press space and type "Curve to Uniform Mesh"
